OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Flate sunshine to end the day, though
OL,7,Fan isolated shower may develop towards
OL,8,Fthe south coast. Dry overnight, with
OL,9,Fclear skies for most. Temperatures
OL,10,Fremaining on the warm side.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny morning cloud clearing to
OL,13,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,14,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Remaining hot, though a
OL,16,Flittle cooler along some coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
